# Azure PostgreSQL Flexible Server

This Terraform module creates an Azure PostgreSQL Flexible Server with minimal resource consumption.

## Resources Created
- Azure Resource Group
- Azure PostgreSQL Flexible Server (B1ms - minimal consumption)
- PostgreSQL Database

## Variables
- `resource_group_name`: Name of the resource group
- `location`: Azure region
- `db_name`: Name of the PostgreSQL Flexible Server
- `database_name`: Name of the PostgreSQL database
- `admin_username`: Administrator username for the database
- `admin_password`: Administrator password (set securely)

## Outputs
- `db_fqdn`: Fully qualified domain name of the database
- `db_admin_username`: Administrator username
- `db_connection_string`: Connection string to connect to the database

